name: Biggie
description: Biggie is a popular Pitbull across several social media platforms, such as Tiktok, Youtube and Instagram. With a blend of creativity and comedic gestures, Biggie brings animal loving entertainment to millions of viewers through images, videos and reels. With Biggie the Pitbull's growing popularity, the meme coin $BIGGIE was inspired and launched on the ethereum network, leveraging Biggies unique sense of humor and style.
